def rmse(y, y_pred):
    # RMSE, Root Mean Square Error, 
    return sqrt(mean_squared_error(y, y_pred))
In [248]:
def data_vis(X, y, y_pred=None, title=''):
    # 
    # plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    plt.plot(X.index, X['#Passengers'], label='X')
    plt.plot(y.index, y['#Passengers'], label='y')
    if y_pred is not None:
        plt.plot(y_pred.index, y_pred['#Passengers'], label=title)
    plt.legend(loc='best')
    plt.xlabel('Month')
    plt.ylabel('#Passengers')
    plt.title(title)
    plt.show()

二、基于统计学的方法¶

2.1 ARIMA 系列¶

2.1.1 AR (AutoRegressive，自回归)¶

$p$

$$ AR(p): \ x_{t}=\phi_{1}x_{t-1}+\phi_{2}x_{t-2}+\cdots+\phi_{p}x_{t-p}+\mu_{t} $$

$_t$ $\phi$

2.2 Exponential Smoothing (指数平滑) 系列¶

ARIMA

ETS ErrorTrendSeasonality

2.2.1 Single Exponential Smoothing (SES，一次指数平滑)¶

$$ s_i=\alpha x_i+(1\alpha)s_i1 $$

$\alpha$ $0 \le \alpha \le 1$

$$ x_{i+h}=s_i $$

$$ \begin{aligned} s_{i}&=\alpha x_{i}+(1-\alpha)s_{i-1} \\ &=\alpha x_{i}+(1-\alpha)[\alpha x_{i-1}+(1-\alpha)s_{i-2}] \\ &=\alpha x_{i}+(1-\alpha)[\alpha x_{i-1}+(1-\alpha)[\alpha x_{i-2}+(1-\alpha)s_{i-3}]] \\ &=\alpha[x_{i}+(1-\alpha)x_{i-1}+(1-\alpha)^{2}x_{i-2}+(1-\alpha)^{3}s_{i-3}] \\ &= \\ &=\alpha\sum_{j=0}^{i}(1-\alpha)^{j}x_{i-j} \end{aligned} $$

In [261]:
#

2.2.2 Double Exponential Smoothing (Holt，二次指数平滑)¶

Trend $t_i$

$$ s_{i}=\alpha x_{i}+(1-\alpha)(s_{i-1}+t_{i-1}) \\ t_{i}=\beta (s_{i}-s_{i-1})+(1-\beta)t_{i-1} $$

$\alpha$ $\beta$ $0 \le \alpha,\beta \le 1$$\alpha$ $\beta$

$$ x_{i+h}=s_{i}+ht_{i} $$

$h$

Addtive TrendMultiplicative Trend

  • Addtive Trend
$$ x_{i+1}=x_i+(x_{i+1}-x_i) $$
  • Multiplicative Trend
$$ x_{i+1}=x_i\frac{x_{i+1}}{x_i} $$
In [263]:

from statsmodels.tsa.api import Holt
 
y_pred = y.copy()

y_pred['#Passengers'] = holt.forecast(len(y))
data_vis(X, y, y_pred, 'Holt Linear')

2.2.3 Triple Exponential Smoothing (三次指数平滑)¶

Seasonality$p_i$

$$ \begin{aligned} s_{i}&=\alpha (x_{i}-p_{i-k})+(1-\alpha)(s_{i-1}+t_{i-1}) \\ t_{i}&=\beta (s_{i}-s_{i-1})+(1-\beta)t_{i-1} \\ p_{i}&=\gamma (x_{i}-s_{i})+(1-\gamma)p_{i-k} \end{aligned} $$

$$ x_{i+h}=s_{i}+ht_{i}+p_{i-k+h} $$

4.4.1 一步单变量 LSTM¶

In [45]:
def split_sequence(sequence, n_steps):
    #  (n_steps, 1) 
    X, y = list(), list()
    for i in range(len(sequence)):
        end_ix = i + n_steps
        if end_ix > len(sequence)-1:
            break
        seq_x, seq_y = sequence[i:end_ix], sequence[end_ix]
        X.append(seq_x)
        y.append(seq_y)
    return np.array(X), np.array(y)
